        <h1 style="text-align: center;">About Us</h1>
          <p class="large_font" style="padding: 0px 20px 0px 20px;">We are the Altamirano's! We are a small, yet growing family business.

Our story is quite unique. A coffee farmer and a yarn lover met and fell in love. So, we decided to put the two together to create something great. We want to share our love for coffee and yarn with you. So you can experience the joy the two bring us! We plan on bringing you quality coffee and quality yarn!

          </p>

          <h4>Meet Harold Altamirano</h4>
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
              <img class="small_photo" src="/assets/img/harold_about_us.jpg">
            </div>
          <p class="large_font" style="padding: 20px">
          Harold was born and raised in Nicaragua and grew up around the beautiful mountainous reserve of Pe&ntilde;as Blancas. Harold came to the U.S. as a teenager to study but never lost his love of coffee. Harold's fondest memories are spending time with his grandmother drinking coffee and sharing stories. He finds joy debating and conversing philosophical theories over a cup of his home coffee. 
          </p>

          <h4>Meet Dulce Altamirano</h4>
          <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
