            </div>
          <p class="large_font" style="padding: 20px;">
          Dulce, the mastermind behind Caf&eacute; Purl. She is California born and raised. She grew up watching her grandmother Petra knit and crochet and learned from her. Her favorite memories were spent knitting or crocheting together with her grandmother and a nice cup of coffee with pan dulce. 
          </p>
        <h1 style="text-align: center;">About Our Coffee</h1>
          <section style="gap: 20px;">
            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
